  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this randomized trial is to investigate the effects of a 12-week yoga intervention
      compared to self-care on quality of life, stress, psychological health, and physiological
      parameters in 77 patients with ulcerative colitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
